{
  "stem": "10587.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were there maybe a day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then the German, the-- I don't know whether it was the Wehrmacht or the SS group, which at that time it was totally confusing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They, they said, we know you are there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we're going count to three.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you don't come out, we will throw in a grenade.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father immediately said, come on, boys.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he went out and raised his arms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He says, [GERMAN SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Don't shoot.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We are coming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and so then they took us to a collecting place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really don't know what exactly happened at the same time to my cousin Jack and, and his, his father, mother, and the, and the-- his younger brother.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But maybe they just remained there for a while, maybe same day, maybe the next day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- because they were satisfied that we came out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we, we were taken to this collecting place, where they put us on a cattle train [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and took us Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a, it was a train that had a roof with-- but it had little [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] openings, you know, for the cattle to be able to breathe.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, you know, they-- when they open the-- I mean, when they lock the door, you get such a click, you know?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that-- I felt like the click in my heart, because I knew where we are going.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] it was very chaotic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were kids, babies, on the floor, my father, myself in the train-- mothers, pregnant women, [CRYING] old people, young people, people my age, people my brother's age.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
